title: The Best Celebrity Photobombs of All Time
text: The Best Celebrity Photobombs of All Time February 27, 2016 12:30 AM 1 / 15 Jessica Biel and Justin Timberlake Photo: Getty Images Even the Oscars aren’t safe from a stealth celebrity photobomb. Just ask Jessica Biel, who was briefly upstaged at this year’s Academy Awards after her husband, Justin Timberlake, popped up out of nowhere behind her and created a hilarious and irresistibly meme-able photo opp. The Timberlakes, of course, aren’t the first celebrities to ruin (or perhaps improve?) a perfectly good step and repeat. Beyoncé, George Clooney, even Queen Elizabeth II have all pulled off the prank flawlessly in the past. Inspired by their sneaky sense of humor, we’ve rounded up our favorite celebrity photobombs of all time—from the Oscars to the Met Gala.
